{"tid":1667970,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[舊聞分享] 過半少數族裔選民有意投票 七成認為無候選人能代表權益","createTime":"2019-10-21T17:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T17:39:53.000Z","uid":220942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b1c0a7c957e7c0631b0d2467a738b10b0a62a34b","tid":1667970,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:39:53.000Z","msg":"劉細良就話林鄭冇理由會因為怕ISIS就即刻去清真寺道歉<br />\n<br />\n咁我就諗一定係背後啲行會成員同<span style=\"color: blue;\">反對民主派</span>(反對派) 求林鄭去道歉, 即係葉劉, 鄭X迅果啲仆街, 佢地1020當晚就好大反應, 似係撩中某啲位<br />\n<br />\n咁我就係咁而睇下少數族裔選民數目<br />\n<br />\n【立會選舉】調查：過半少數族裔選民有意投票 七成認為無候選人能代表權益<br />\n<br />\n本港少數族裔成人人口達14萬人，香港社會服務聯會（社聯）及香港基督教服務處少數族裔服務進行的研究顯示，超過一半合資格少數族裔選民（55%）有意於今次立法會選舉中投票，不過七成人認為沒有候選人能代表他們的權益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20160823/s00001/1471944170814/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E3%80%91%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%8A%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B8%E6%97%8F%E8%A3%94%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8-%E4%B8%83%E6%88%90%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E7%84%A1%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%BA%E8%83%BD%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%AC%8A%E7%9B%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20160823%2Fs00001%2F1471944170814%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B0%2591%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2597%258F%25E8%25A3%2594%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8-%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2580%2599%25E9%2581%25B8%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%259B%258A&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNooeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=b5e11f49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20160823%2Fs00001%2F1471944170814%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B0%2591%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2597%258F%25E8%25A3%2594%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8-%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2580%2599%25E9%2581%25B8%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%259B%258A&h=b429e76c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20160823/s00001/1471944170814/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E3%80%91%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%8A%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B8%E6%97%8F%E8%A3%94%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8-%E4%B8%83%E6%88%90%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E7%84%A1%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%BA%E8%83%BD%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%AC%8A%E7%9B%8A</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我當14萬人50%等於 7 萬人<br />\n7萬人分佢反對派 一半都3萬幾, 再加上通常少數族裔既選區都好集中係某幾區 , 都應該係好重要既票源<br />\n所我地應該要we connect</span>"}]}